VPC
CIDR --> Classless inter-domain Routing

0.0.0.0/0 --> All IPs

11111111 --> 255
0.0.0.0 - 255.255.255.255


0.0.0.0 --> Base IP
/0 --> Subnet Mask

VPC --> 172.31.0.0/16 

Total number of ip addresses denoted by CIDR -->  2^16 (32-16=16) --> 65K+

172.31.0.0/32 --> 1

172.31.0.0/31 --> 2
172.31.0.0/30 --> 4
/29 --> 8
/30 --> 16
/0 --> 2^32


